Invocation Name: jefferson park train tracker
des: Use this skill is to notify a user when the next trains to downtown Chicago will be arriving in Jefferson Park. Say 'Alexa, Ask Jefferson Park Train Tracker when's the next train to downtown' or, 'Alexa, Ask Jefferson Park Train Tracker next train time'
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
